1. Go to Directory "installDir/GameData/movies/".

2. Copy the files "LECIntro.avi" and "NVIDIAIntro.avi" to another Backup-Directory.

3. Delete the both files from the directory "installDir/GameData/movies/".

4. Use the crack #4 from gamecopyworld.
